Drop the official partner logos here for the 502 Demo Day page.

Name each file after the partner id, any image format works
(.svg recommended, also .png / .webp / .jpg / .avif):

  502.svg        -> The 502 Project
  barrilete.svg  -> Barrilete Ventures
  notion.svg     -> Notion

The page auto-detects them and swaps the text wordmark for the real logo.
Prefer light/white versions since they sit on a near-black background.
